##########File Description###########
SH2_R24_SUM_fre_regression: Dataset with log(ratio) values of all sequences in R24 library
SH2_R24_SUM_fre_regression_balance: Balanced regression dataset, with samples where log(ratio) > 0 equal to those where log(ratio) <= 0
SH2_R24_SUM_fre_regression_balance_train: Training and validation data for the regression model
SH2_R24_SUM_fre_regression_balance_test: Test data for the regression model